  {
    "language": "en",
    "text": "A device comprising one or more heat transfer laminates each including an electrode, a first dielectric layer on a first side of the electrode, and a second dielectric layer on a second side of the electrode; a plurality of flexible electrocaloric elements, each of the flexible electrocaloric elements including an electrocaloric material layer, a flexible electrode layer on the electrocaloric layer, one or more fixed portions each attached to one of heat transfer laminates, and a movable portion that is movable with respect to the one of the heat transfer laminates.",
    "truncated": false
  },
  {
    "language": "en",
    "text": "A device comprising one or more heat transfer laminates each including an electrode, a first dielectric layer on a first side of the electrode, and a second dielectric layer on a second side of the electrode; a plurality of flexible electrocaloric elements, each of the flexible electrocaloric elements including an electrocaloric material layer, a flexible electrode layer on the electrocaloric layer, one or more fixed portions each attached to one of heat transfer laminates, and a movable portion that is movable with respect to the one of the heat transfer laminates.",
    "truncated": false
  }
